About the GameYou inherited a ranch in the wooded mountains, which you can completely upgrade and customize.
Key Features
Improving and building your own ranch;
Fully open world;
Many types of livestock and wild animals;
Hunting and protection of your territory from predatory forest animals;
Several types of fully customizable vehicles;
Mini games
Radio stations with great music;
Day&Night cycle;
